Iain S. Berdzar Age 43

El Cajon, CA | Escondido, CA | Ramona, CA

Iain Berdzar lives in El Cajon, California. Other places in which he has lived are Escondido, California; Ramona, California; Dolores, Colorado and Broomfield, Colorado. He attended the Fort Lewis College, Pueblo Community College and Ramona High School. He works at Swca Environmental Consultants. Iain loves listening to Pixies, Millencolin, The Clash, The Ramones, Social Distortion, Alkaline Trio, The Pixies and Johnny Cash. Some of his favorite TV shows are Espn, My Name Is Earl, Dirty Jobs, The History Channel, Crocodile Hunter, Lonesome Dove and Espn 2. Gladiator, Blue Velvet, Blazing Saddles, Open Range, Jeremiah Johnson, Fat City and Spaceballs are among his all-time favorite films. Peter Francis Berdzar, Colin Brett Berdzar, Jacklyn Marie Berdzar, Cleave C Berdzar, Loren Blaise Berdzar and Taralyn G Berdzar are in Iain family.
